# Git commits

When creating git commits for this repository:

- **Author**: `Lokesh-UE <lokesh.chamakuri@ue-germany.de>` only
- **Never** add `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>` or any Cursor/agent trailer
- **Never** use `iqearners`, `iqearnersteam@gmail.com`, or `cursoragent` as author or co-author
- Use plain commit messages with no co-author lines unless the user explicitly requests a co-author
